{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you take on the role of a exorcist to complete a ritual. As the spirits struggle and various sinister disruptions arise, you must hold your ground until the ritual is complete and successfully banish them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Duration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can choose your game duration at the start:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20 minutes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Duration selection does not affect achievement unlocking.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spirit Pursuit</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wandering vengeful ghosts will attempt to capture you, testing your courage and strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Toy Destruction</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spirit-controlled dolls will try to sabotage the barrier\u2014you must act quickly to stop them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diverse Disruptions</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of minor and major disturbances keep the tension and challenge levels high.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Narrative-Free Focus</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A pure game-play experience that dives straight into the core fun.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Modes &amp; Maps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Easy Mode</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Faster stamina recovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only one doll on the field, reducing difficulty.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hard Mode</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Offers additional collection achievements for hardcore players seeking deeper satisfaction.</p></li></ul><p c